{"tid":1964082,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國留學] 自修SAT/ACT","createTime":"2020-04-08T14:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T01:11:31.000Z","uid":119810,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"48659528360709318741f16e4e40ccb94a0c7d8f","tid":1964082,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:23:17.000Z","msg":"如果文科人係咪應該考SAT 因為ACT要考science 同埋聽講SAT比較多學校accept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但啲人又話ACT容易啲<br />\n<br />\nsubject test/AP係咪必須？<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩練習推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n考黎打算做個backup 但係好冇方向 唔知應該由邊度開始 數底真係好差 全部嘢都要重新學過 想問點樣溫習做好 我打算年尾或者年頭考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇巴絲打報過princeton review online class？係咪真係有用？<br />\n<br />\nthankyou<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dba1afad7a868edf431b755e199b21268c3683d","tid":1964082,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805db80cab06109c6af1633904bcfd31f577ec12","tid":1964082,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1dba1afad7a868edf431b755e199b21268c3683d","tid":1964082,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"睇左 但我數學由中三開始就一直都好差 去到紐西蘭讀書啲數學係完全唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nvocab有冇specific一個list？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今年yr13 開左學一個月左右 但我呢邊係12月畢業 我讀ncea 就係因為咁搞到我啲時間好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n報越好嘅嘢 你意思係ap/subjecttest？巴打你會建議考邊個好 我係呢邊讀開econ business sociology 係咪應該揀ap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cr